msgstr "Normaal · Lichte stoornis · Matige stoornis · Ernstige stoornis"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "**Communication**"
msgstr "**Communicatie**"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "Normal · Difficulty · Non-verbal · Aphasia"
msgstr "Normaal · Moeilijkheid · Non-verbaal · Afasie"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:103
msgid "Senses and risks"
msgstr "De zintuigen en de risico's"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:105
msgid "The **Senses & Risk Assessment** section completes the profile:"
msgstr "De sectie **Zintuigen & risicobeoordeling** vervolledigt het profiel:"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "**Vision**"
msgstr "**Visie**"

#: ../../content/soins/dossier-medical.md:81
msgid "Normal · Corrected (Glasses) · Impaired · Blind"
